title: Law of Attraction - Explained in Under 3 Minutes
itunes:title: Law of Attraction - Explained in Under 3 Minutes
description:
Episode 294 - Still confused about the law of attraction? Here is my quickest and simplest way of explaining how to use it in your life! After listening to this, ask yourself what am I attracting into my life that I do not want and what do I want to start attracting into my life by changing my thoughts?
